## Get Repo Info
```console
helm repo add 3bit-techs https://3bit-techs.github.io/helm-charts
helm repo update
```

## Install Chart
```console
helm install [RELEASE_NAME] 3bit-techs/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

## Configuration
```console
helm show values 3bit-techs/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

## Upgrading Chart
```console
helm upgrade [RELEASE_NAME] 3bit-techs/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

## Uninstall Chart
```console
helm uninstall [RELEASE_NAME]
```

